title: THE JACK BENNY PROGRAM -- with Hugh Downs and Rock Hudson
description:
This 1962 episode has a parody of Jack's Paar's "The Tonight Show" with 
Jack Benny playing the part of Paar, shortly before Johnny Carson took over 
the daily late night time NBC slot and Jack Paar moved into prime-time once a week. 
The original videotape of this show was supposedly erased by CBS, and as with the previously uploaded Billy Graham episode and another one...this kinescope film was remastered by the UCCA Film Archive.  It's one of several released on "The Jack Benny Program - The Lost Episodes" DVD set in June 2013.
